SELECT contestant_id, name FROM contestant_profiles WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 30 ORDER BY contestant_id

SELECT cp.contestant_name, co.competition_date FROM contestant_profiles cp INNER JOIN competition_outcomes co ON cp.contestant_id = co.contestant_id WHERE cp.age < 30 ORDER BY co.competition_date DESC
SELECT cp.contestant_name, co.rank FROM contestant_profiles cp LEFT JOIN competition_outcomes co ON cp.contestant_id = co.contestant_id WHERE co.rank <= 3

SELECT * FROM contestant_profiles WHERE contestant_age < 30 ORDER BY contestant_name DESC;
SELECT contestant_name, contestant_experience FROM contestant_profiles WHERE contestant_experience IS NOT NULL;

SELECT contestant_id, COUNT(outcome_id) AS total_outcomes FROM contestant_profiles LEFT JOIN competition_outcomes ON contestant_profiles.contestant_id = competition_outcomes.contestant_id GROUP BY contestant_id HAVING total_outcomes > 3;

SELECT contestant_name, outcome_description FROM contestant_profiles JOIN competition_outcomes ON contestant_profiles.contestant_id = competition_outcomes.contestant_id WHERE competition_round = 2 AND outcome_description LIKE '%positive%';
SELECT contestant_name, AVG(contestant_age) AS avg_age FROM contestant_profiles GROUP BY contestant_name HAVING avg_age > 25;
SELECT * FROM contestant_profiles;
SELECT contestant_name, contestant_age FROM contestant_profiles WHERE contestant_country = 'USA';
SELECT judge_name, judge_specialty FROM judges ORDER BY judge_name DESC;

SELECT * FROM contestant_profiles;
SELECT contestant_name, contestant_country FROM contestant_profiles WHERE contestant_age > 25;
SELECT c.contestant_name, co.competition_date, co.placement FROM contestant_profiles c JOIN competition_outcomes co ON c.contestant_id = co.contestant_id;
SELECT c.contestant_name, j.judge_name, j.judge_specialty FROM contestant_profiles c JOIN judge_feedback jf ON c.contestant_id = jf.contestant_id JOIN judges j ON jf.judge_id = j.judge_id;

SELECT c.contestant_name, co.placement, j.judge_name, jf.feedback_text FROM contestant_profiles c JOIN competition_outcomes co ON c.contestant_id = co.contestant_id JOIN judge_feedback jf ON c.contestant_id = jf.contestant_id JOIN judges j ON jf.judge_id = j.judge_id WHERE co.placement <= 3 ORDER BY co.placement ASC;
